short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Daily astronomy photos courtesy of NASA.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
APOD New Tab Page uses NASA's Astronomy Picture of The Day service to display the daily astronomy photo on your new tab page. Along with the beautiful photos and interface, you will also get the description of the daily photo to read.

How to use:
Toggle seconds in time - click time
Toggle description - click extension icon

I hope you enjoy this extension, if you like or dislike this extension, feel free to leave a review. All feedback is appreciated and taken into consideration.
